Knight (Europe)
A warrior of the old European tradition, schooled in chivalry, honor, and the
knightly arts in the magical lands of post-Rifts Europe. European Knights serve
lords and kingdoms that survived the apocalypse behind walls of magic and steel.

Starting skills: Horsemanship, body building, climbing, first aid, lore magic,
W.P. two ancient, W.P. two modern, plus elective picks from Military, Physical,
Technical, and W.P. categories.

Attribute requirements: PS 12, PE 12, MA 10.
Starting equipment: Full plate or chainmail (enchanted if noble lineage), two
ancient weapons, one ranged weapon, horse, and knightly crest.
Starting credits: 500 credits (standard kit).
PPE / ISP: No starting PPE or ISP.

